Hello, this is my new and first zm_ map.
zm_corpse is a scary-based map with many dark areas and fitting light.
Nothing else to say except one thing: This map is not **playtested** because i have no friends (insert sad smylie).
If you have some **improvements**, feel free to post them and i will do my best.
___________

-2 Custom Soundscapes
